<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.182359>
    dc:description "FIGURE 9. Genital structures of Cotithene species, from left to right: aedeagus, ventral view; aedeagus, lateral view; posterior region of female sternum VIII, ventral view; spermatheca, lateral view; shaded areas depicting structures of the internal sac. A, C. dicranopygia; B, C. stratiotricha." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/182359/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

